    "Location": "",
    "cnAction": "叼着棒棒糖，苦笑",
    "cnWords": "在Kirkland的时候我天天替他们洗白。他们白天在教堂高喊道德，晚上在地下赌场输得精光。Webb只是把这门生意做得更系统化——他有流程表。",
    "enAction": "Lollipop in mouth, bitter smile",
    "enWords": "At Kirkland, I whitewashed them every day. By day they shout morals in church, by night they lose everything in underground casinos. Webb just systematized the business—he had flowcharts.",
