    "Location": "",
    "cnAction": "耸肩",
    "cnWords": "因为这城市只信两样东西——钱和权力。正义？那是穷人讲给自己听的睡前故事。",
    "enAction": "Shrugs",
    "enWords": "Because this city only believes in two things—money and power. Justice? That's a bedtime story poor people tell themselves.",
